Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:03.75,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}O interior do coração é um mistério.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:05.37,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Estrelas e a neve brilham ao nosso redor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:07.13,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Uma escura e calma noite de neve,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.09,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}mas aparece um guerreiro assustador de armadura!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:10.92,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ele vê a única verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.80,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Com a aparência de uma criança, mas a mente de um adulto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:14.55,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Seu nome é Detetive Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:24.39,RMLyrics10,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be4}futari-dake no toki  itsumo ienai-kara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:33.60,RMLyrics10,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be4}chiisa na KISS  toki o tomete  kono mama
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.32,RMLyrics10,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be4}Need your love tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:48.67,RMLyrics10,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be4}sagashite-ita unmei no shunkan o  deatta kimi to futari
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:01:00.18,RMLyrics10,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be4}omoidasu  yuki no houmu  kimi no kage ga  chiisakunaru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:07.10,RMLyrics10,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be4}zutto  anata ni ageru yo  winter bell
